				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=96992&amp;sid=d85f896d28606ccdcb70389d1d4d0da4#96992"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Mon Nov 15, 2004 7:11 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Should we just hand the country over to New Englanders?</span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=96992&amp;sid=d85f896d28606ccdcb70389d1d4d0da4"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
