By your logic, we should have no police, firemen, public schools, etc. Basic rights are protected and enforced (ideally) already... so why not basic rights to life? Like anything else, rights need to be fought for.
<br />
Making sure everyone is at least basically healthy will help out society as a whole as well. It's not just for that one person, it helps stop infection, gets people treated when they need it, etc.
<br />

